不让想自己变成我讨厌的模样。 甚至，如果说，这个世界，必须要靠虚伪才能运行下去的话。 「我才不稀罕在这种世界里活下去！」"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "85 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/472584199"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4Iuv/j1YCE2aVdEAMaCDY3Mjk4MTI4IJv0xIcGMAE4XkAkcgk0NzI1ODQxOTl4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "37_1627225321.5549388", "card_id": "Q_31025946", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 297}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "长沙有哪些深藏不露的餐馆？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "那些很出名的像黑色经典臭豆腐，向群锅饺都吃过了，求推荐些有特色的美食和好吃的小店~"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/907a11d04f35007f7253c763c5d402f5_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "70 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/31025946"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4Iuv/j1YCE2aVdEAMaBzQ1OTMwMTEg54bMqwUwCDi0qQFAJXIIMzEwMjU5NDZ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "38_1627225321.5553894", "card_id": "Q_447892619", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 22}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "在中国都发现过哪些「独特的古生物」?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "中国地方那么大，曾经生活在这里的古生物应该也很多又有意思吧"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-46db2f128017f5d5089aaf3da8722feb_1440w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "69 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/447892619"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Iuv/j1YCE2aVdEAMaCDYxODEwMzQyIOa8jIIGMAM4ngFAJnIJNDQ3ODkyNjE5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "39_1627225321.5561125", "card_id": "Q_474561301", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 519}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待追光动画制作的《青蛇劫起》上映口碑两极分化？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "是什么原因导致追光一直处于尴尬的局面，难道追光真的就做不出来爆款